[{"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "この城は……学院の図書室にあった、太古の建物と酷似している……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "でも、この城の素材……、遥か昔に失われたはずなのに、いったいどうして……ううん……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "なぁユーディル。妙な奴が、城の壁に向かってぶつぶつしゃべってるんだが……知り合いか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "……いや、初めて見る顔だな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "なあ、きみ。ここでなにをしてるんだ？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "そもそも、この辺りにこのような城があったという資料はなかったはず……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "それなのに、どうして――。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "……まるで聞こえてねーみたいだな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "えっと、きみ。ちょっといいかな？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "うひゃあっ!?　え、な、なんですか……、あなたたち……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0047.wav"], "content": "驚かせてすまない。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "おれたち、この城に住んでるんだけど、きみがなにしてるのかなと思ってさ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "あ……こ、この城の方でしたか。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0047.wav"], "content": "す、すみませんでした！勝手に城を調べていて……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "ボクは、ニコラっていいます。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "えと、『学院』の生徒で……、決して、怪しいものではないですから。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "ん……学院……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "もしかして、ギルドが運営している、『魔法学院』のことか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "ランザーヴ。学院って、なんだ？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "魔法の才能がある奴らを集めて、英才教育を行ってる学校のことだ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "完全な実力主義で、天才的な魔法の素質を認められないと、入学すら許されないって話だ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "へぇ……ということは、ニコラは優秀な魔法使いなんだな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "いえ……ボクなんて全然……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0020.wav"], "content": "いつも、周りについていくだけで、必死なくらいですから。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0043.wav"], "content": "で？　学院の生徒が城の壁にへばりついてなにしてたんだ？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "えっと、学院の授業の一環で、研究の題材になるものを探していたら、この城を見つけまして……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0020.wav"], "content": "この城には、今は失われた建築技術や、古代の貴重な建築資材が使われていたので、珍しくてつい……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "あ、あの……あなたたちは、この城の所有者なんですよね？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "よろしければ……その、この城をボクの研究対象にさせてもらえませんか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "ああ。構わないよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "きみみたいな真面目な学生なら、断る理由はないからね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0022.wav"], "content": "ほ、本当ですか!?このご恩は、一生忘れません！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "それでは、早速調査させていただきますね！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "ただ、城の周りには、夜になると魔獣が出るから、気をつけたほうが――", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "しかし、どうしてこうも太古の建物がここまで見事に現存していたんだろうか……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0074.wav"], "content": "……って、聞いてるか？おーい。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "この城の材質、もしかして、魔法で建物の劣化を食い止めていた？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "いや、それ以外にも――。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "聞こえてないみたいだな……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "すげぇ集中力だ。さすがは学院の生徒、ってところか。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110025011, "title": "魔法学院の生徒"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "……ふぅ。今日の素振りは、これくらいにしておくか……ん？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "なるほど……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0001.wav"], "content": "やっとわかったぞ、この城にまったく劣化が見られない理由が……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "ニコラ……？どうした、大きな声出して。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "え、あ、ユーディルさん！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "聞いてください！　この城について、大変なことがわかったんです！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "大変なこと……？　あー、でも、その話は、顔拭いてからにしないか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "顔中、ホコリまみれだぞ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "え、うわっ。本当だ……。全然気づきませんでした……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "あはは。相変わらず、すごい集中力だな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "……それで、大変なことって？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "あ、それがですね！　城のマナ反応が、『極東の尖塔』の72階で出た数値と完全に一致したんですよ！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "『古城の歴史書』第108項の記述によれば、『極東の尖塔』は、魔法の発明より200年は前に作られたもので……、", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "同様の反応が見られた、という記述は、『聖地図』26項、『巡礼書』15項にしかない、非常に稀なものなんです！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0074.wav"], "content": "えーっと……内容に関しては、あんまりよくわからなかったけど……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "ナントカ書の第何項に書かれてるとか、ナントカ書の数値と同じとか……、どうしてすぐにわかるんだ？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "確かめているにしては、よどみがないし……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "ああ。以前、学院の蔵書で読んだ時に書いてあったことなんです。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "蔵書で読んだ、って……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "まさかニコラ、今まで読んだ本の内容、一字一句覚えてるのか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "はい。何度も何度も、読み返して覚えたんです。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0017.wav"], "content": "そうなのか……。やっぱりすごいな、ニコラは。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "いえ……ボクは天才じゃないから、せめて知識を武器にしようと思って、たくさん本を読んだだけですよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "天才じゃない……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "きみほどの知識があるなら、それはもう才能だと思うんだけど。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0035.wav"], "content": "いえ、天才と呼ばれるような人たちは、ボクと違って、本を読み漁ったり、事前に準備をしたりはしませんよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "ボクが何日もかけて完成させた魔法を、練習もなく一瞬でやってのけるんです。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0020.wav"], "content": "……ボクには、とてもかないません。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "なるほどな……その気持ち、わかるよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "おれも昔から、兄上たちに剣術の腕で全然かなわなくてさ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "ユーディルさんが……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0028.wav"], "content": "それこそ、信じられませんよ。あんなに強いのに……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "兄上たちに負け続けた分、必死に努力してきたからな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "そこそこの腕には、なったと思うよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "でも、もしおれが、才能のある剣士に見えているなら、おれから見たきみだって、才能のある魔法使いだよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "え……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "きみが今の知識を手にするまでには、きっと、おれには想像もつかないほどの努力をしてきたんだと思う。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "それは、生まれ持ったものじゃないかもしれないけど……、立派な才能なんだと、おれは思うよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "努力が、才能……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "そんなふうに考えたこと……今まで、一度もなかったです……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "……でも確かに、努力の量なら誰にも負けない自信があります。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "それが、ボクの才能だったんですね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110025012, "title": "ニコラの才能"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "グルルルルル……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120007_01.png", "speakerName": "魔獣", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "くっ……落ち着け、ボク……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "魔獣のことなら……、本でたくさん学んだはずだ……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "『魔獣録』第22項……。森で魔獣と遭遇した時には、高台に陣取り、頭上から……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0056.wav"], "content": "うわあっ!?", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0075.wav"], "content": "ま、まずい、低地に追い込まれた……。こういう時は、日差しを背に――", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0002.wav"], "content": "おい、ニコラ！さっきからなに喋ってるんだ！戦闘に集中しないと、怪我するぞ！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0047.wav"], "content": "う……はい、すみません……。それと、助かりました……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "……ったく。まあ、無事でよかったけどな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "…………。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0024.wav"], "content": "ふう……。魔獣は、倒しきれたみたいだな。みんな、怪我はないか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "……はい、大丈夫です。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0047.wav"], "content": "あの、すみませんでした……。全然、戦いの役に立てなくて……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "役に立ってないとまでは言わないが……戦闘中に、なにかぶつぶつ言ってたろ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "ありゃ、いったいなんなんだ？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "それは、その……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "魔獣のことは本で学んでいたので、それを、思い出していたんです。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "でも……いくら頭でわかっていても、いざ魔獣を前にすると、体が動かなくて……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "やっぱり、ダメですね……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "知識だけあっても、実戦ではなんの役にも立ちません。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "そういうことか……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "なあニコラ。魔獣と戦った経験は、どれくらいあるんだ？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "……ほとんどないです。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "なら、今回うまくやれなかったのは、仕方ないんじゃねーか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "え……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "俺だって、実戦で訓練通りに戦えるようになるまでには、かなり時間がかかったぞ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "ランザーヴさんが？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "信じられません……、あんなに強いのに……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "何度も実戦を繰り返して、経験を積んで、それでやっと、今みたいに戦えるようになったんだよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "もちろん、実戦だけでもダメだがな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "訓練で身につけた知識と技術があって、初めて、実戦経験が役に立つんだ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "だから俺は……お前が持ってるその知識、これから実戦経験を積めば、ものすごい武器になると思うぞ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "ランザーヴさん……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0071.wav"], "content": "不慣れなうちは、俺たちが援護してやるから、ゆっくり経験を積めばいい。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100003_story/VO_CHR_100003_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "お前の知識が、いつか俺たちみんなを助けてくれる、すごい武器になるって、俺は信じてるからな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100003_01.png", "speakerName": "ランザーヴ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0046.wav"], "content": "あ……ありがとうございます……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "いつかきっと……ボクの知識で、皆さんのお役に立ってみせます！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……あの、ユーディルさん。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "これからはもっと、ボクを実戦に参加させてくれませんか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0071.wav"], "content": "早く、たくさん実戦経験を積みたいんです。お願いします！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "ああ。もちろんだよ。頼りにしてるからな、ニコラ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110025013, "title": "知識を武器に"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "302……！　303……！304……！　305……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "……ん？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "ニコラ。洗濯物、取り込んでるのか？おれも手伝おうか。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "いえ、もう終わりますから、ユーディルさんは訓練を続けていてください。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0027.wav"], "content": "そうか、じゃあお言葉に甘えて。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0074.wav"], "content": "……っと、何回までやったっけ？ま、いいか。また1からやれば。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "……ユーディルさんって、毎日欠かさず、剣の訓練をしていますよね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "ああ。毎日続けないと、すぐに腕がなまるからな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……あの、ひとつ聞いていいですか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "ん？なんだ？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "ユーディルさんは、お兄さんたちに負け続けて……自分は弱いって感じていたんですよね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "ああ。それがどうかしたか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "正直、信じられません。ここにいる騎士の方たちと比べても、見劣りするとは思えませんし……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "この前の戦いでも、魔獣相手に、勇敢に戦っていたじゃないですか。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "まあ、今は訓練の甲斐あって、そこそこ戦えるけど。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0020.wav"], "content": "でも、訓練を始めた頃はひどかったぞ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "必死に訓練してきたのに、その日初めて剣を持った騎士見習いに、模擬戦で完敗したりとかな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "え……。そんな経験をしたのに、どうして訓練を続けてこられたんですか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "……諦めたくなかったんだよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "あそこで努力することまでやめたら、きっと誰にも追いつけなくなるし。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "それに、おれが続けたくて続けてるんだから、誰にどう思われようと関係ないからな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "……ユーディルさんは、すごいですね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "ボクもそんなふうに、夢に向かって突き進めたらいいな……。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "夢？ニコラ、夢があるのか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "はい。……きっと笑われるから、まだ誰にも言ったことないんですけど。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "おれは笑わないよ、約束する。だから、よかったら聞かせてくれないか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0027.wav"], "content": "……わかりました。えっと、その、ボクはいつか、世の中の誰もが、魔法を使える世界を作りたいんです。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "誰もが、魔法を使える世界……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "はい。特別な才能がなくても、努力と訓練次第で、魔法は扱えるって、みんなに証明したいんです。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "それは、天才じゃないからこそ……魔法の才能がないボクだからこそ、できることかなって、思うんです。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "なるほどな……。それは、すごくニコラらしい、いい夢だと思う。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0022.wav"], "content": "ほ、本当ですか……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0012.wav"], "content": "ああ。誰より努力してるきみなら、きっと叶えられるよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "できることがあれば、おれも協力する。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100001_01.png", "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0046.wav"], "content": "あ、ありがとうございます……！ボク、ユーディルさんを見習って、頑張ります！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0071.wav"], "content": "誰になんと言われようと、諦めずに……必ずやり遂げてみせますから！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110025014, "title": "天才じゃないからこそ"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "ニコラ、ちょっといいか？きみ宛に、手紙が届いてるぞ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "手紙、ですか？　……ああ、学院からですね。ずいぶん早かったな。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "学院から……？なんの手紙なのか、聞いてもいいか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "はい。実はボク、学院に休学届を出しまして……この手紙は、その返答です。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0021.wav"], "content": "休学、認めてもらえたみたいです。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "まあ、学院では期待されてなかったし、引き止められる理由はないですからね。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0007.wav"], "content": "ちょ、ちょっと待ってくれ。休学って、どういうことだ？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "それは……そろそろ、学院に戻らなきゃいけなかったんですけど、ボクはまだ、この城に留まりたくて。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "いいのか……？城では、魔法は学べないと思うぞ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "確かに、魔法は学べないかもしれないですけど……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "でもボクは、この城で、大切なことをたくさん学べたと思うんです。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "この城で学んだことは、どれも、教科書や学院の授業では、決して学べないことばかりでした。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "自分とはまったく違う経験をしている人の考え方や、学院にいては会えないような人たちの話を聞いて……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "努力の形も、才能の形も、ひとつじゃないんだって、知ることができました。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "ボクが今まで、たくわえてきた知識が才能なんだって思えたのも、この城で暮らせたおかげなんです。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0062.wav"], "content": "……でも、ニコラ、それは……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……もしかして、ボクなんかが城に留まるのは、ご迷惑ですか……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "いや……。城に残るのは構わないよ。でも、きみの夢はどうするんだ？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "前に話してくれたじゃないか、世の中の誰もが、魔法を使える世界を作る、って。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "そのためには……、この城に留まるより、学院で魔法を学んだほうがいいんじゃないのか？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "いいえ。夢を叶えるために、ボクはこの城に留まりたいんです。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "この城でしばらく暮らして……、ここでの経験こそ、ボクには必要だと思ったんです。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "ボクは天才ではありませんから、これからも努力を続けて、知識を増やしていくしかない。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "だから、同じように努力を続けているユーディルさんの近くで、頑張りたいんです。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "あなたを見習って、努力を重ねれば、いつか天才にも負けない知識を手に入れて……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "夢を叶えられるような、立派な魔法使いになれるって、ボクは、そう思うんです。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "だから……この城に留まるのは、ボクの夢への第一歩なんです！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0027.wav"], "content": "そうか……。そういうことなら、ニコラ。おれはきみを歓迎するよ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "きみの夢のために必要なことがあれば、どんなことでも言ってくれ。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100001_story/VO_CHR_100001_STORY_0071.wav"], "content": "おれは、なんだって協力するから。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "ユーディル", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0046.wav"], "content": "ユーディルさん……。ありがとうございます！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "これからも、お世話になります！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_110025_story/VO_CHR_110025_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "ボク……ボク……、絶対に、夢を叶えてみせますから！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/110025_01.png", "speakerName": "ニコラ", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 110025015, "title": "努力が咲かす夢"}]